longBusinessSummary: Axolot Solutions Holding AB (publ) provides solutions for industrial water purification in Sweden. The company offers AxoPur, a water purification system. It also provides industries solutions, including smelting, chemical, and paper and pulp; painting, surface treatment, and metalworking; dairies, slaughterhouses, and fish farming/fish slaughterhouses; smaller treatment plant and leachate landfill; and stormwater, sludge suction water, leachate water, and vehicle wash. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Helsingborg, Sweden.
